{"tid":2070491,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【35+初選】印裔社工Jeffrey Andrews希望九西選民幫手提名","createTime":"2020-06-19T07:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T01:54:40.000Z","uid":138409,"like":47,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"1fcda802537e46bff4087397e793c309cf020b55","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jeffreyandrews20/photos/a.112621337160126/114444256977834/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjeffreyandrews20%2Fphotos%2Fa.112621337160126%2F114444256977834%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=204adff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jeffreyandrews20/photos/a.112621337160126/114444256977834/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n💣緊急緊急！<br />\n我哋需要200九西選民簽名，目前只收集到20個😭😢快啲嚟搵我哋啦！<br />\n<br />\nJeffrey喺全港第一個註冊印裔社工，呢個土生土長香港人默默喺15年來，做無數社區工作，撐少數族裔，撐無家者，撐任何手足，為公義、為平等發聲。請支持Jeffrey Andrews，我哋喺今日之內，需要你嘅簽名。<br />\n<br />\n🎤街站<br />\n時間：中午12點至凌晨12點<br />\n地點：尖沙咀iSquare正門（8點後轉場重慶大廈）<br />\n<br />\n自介：<br />\n我喺Jeffrey Andrews, 在香港土生土長嘅第一位印度裔社工。<br />\n過去十一年，我秉持着&quot;Keep serving those in need&quot;呢個理念，致力服務香港弱勢群體。<br />\n今時今日，放眼全球，種族衝突仍然時有發生。香港作為一個多元化國際城市，不同種族之間雖能共處，卻仍然存有誤解，並未能真正共融。不少土生土長嘅非華裔香港人仍被視為外來者，他們喺語言、教育、工作上都受到極大阻礙。<br />\n我對少數族裔嘅經歷身同感受，因此，我期望自己能成為不同族裔群體之間嘅橋樑，促進種族共融，並向世界推廣香港並不局限於國際金融中心，而喺一個擁抱多元文化，普世價值嘅國際都會，呢個獨特嘅香港值得被珍惜。<br />\n我誠邀所有香港人，與我站在同一陣線，為香港爭取民主自由和種族平等，建立一個更理想嘅家園。<br />\n<br />\n初選步驟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEr5rUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEr5rUM.jpg&h=425bbd47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e75e49abb83f9d2a68f8d51fe58a5f40c89c5ee","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf967323ace7a0ef92fd8a07f0f1f0c9eae4324","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"25e7a26675049dcc725943d7a5c7ffd88b95bea8","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"aa8e3d37689658cf4ec1a5f911eaa1d624353a74","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb8c9b3142da686bc8a797664b1342afbc208727","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9b884d81b621fbc8b291448235f2ad294d0a68f5","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ae6e59da99fd866617bb3fba0c73e97c10be482","tid":2070491,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84438daf22eb0cb1fef77bb1f37c62185860df80","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"669ec3c5d5f461b79cb21ee62e00527395fdc2da","tid":2070491,"uid":56326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" 