6-19T08:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d97daf00ee9b29a26df66c6c0605822450cb6dc","tid":2070491,"uid":203397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fcda802537e46bff4087397e793c309cf020b55","tid":2070491,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jeffreyandrews20/photos/a.112621337160126/114444256977834/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjeffreyandrews20%2Fphotos%2Fa.112621337160126%2F114444256977834%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=204adff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jeffreyandrews20/photos/a.112621337160126/114444256977834/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n💣緊急緊急！<br />\n我哋需要200九西選民簽名，目前只收集到20個😭😢快啲嚟搵我哋啦！<br />\n<br />\nJeffrey喺全港第一個註冊印裔社工，呢個土生土長香港人默默喺15年來，做無數社區工作，撐少數族裔，撐無家者，撐任何手足，為公義、為平等發聲。請支持Jeffrey Andrews，我哋喺今日之內，需要你嘅簽名。<br />\n<br />\n🎤街站<br />\n時間：中午12點至凌晨12點<br />\n地點：尖沙咀iSquare正門（8點後轉場重慶大廈）<br />\n<br />\n自介：<br />\n我喺Jeffrey Andrews, 在香港土生土長嘅第一位印度裔社工。<br />\n過去十一年，我秉持着&quot;Keep serving those in need&quot;呢個理念，致力服務香港弱勢群體。<br />\n今時今日，放眼全球，種族衝突仍然時有發生。香港作為一個多元化國際城市，不同種族之間雖能共處，卻仍然存有誤解，並未能真正共融。不少土生土長嘅非華裔香港人仍被視為外來者，他們喺語言、教育、工作上都受到極大阻礙。<br />\n我對少數族裔嘅經歷身同感受，因此，我期望自己能成為不同族裔群體之間嘅橋樑，促進種族共融，並向世界推廣香港並不局限於國際金融中心，而喺一個擁抱多元文化，普世價值嘅國際都會，呢個獨特嘅香港值得被珍惜。<br />\n我誠邀所有香港人，與我站在同一陣線，為香港爭取民主自由和種族平等，建立一個更理想嘅家園。<br />\n<br />\n初選步驟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEr5rUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEr5rUM.jpg&h=425bbd47&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"15年，搵番班印度手足簽仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n洗鬼上來做乞丐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa021524900325b2775135c8742fe9c3940d1b9","tid":2070491,"uid":346806,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"講真咁多年都冇一個南亞人代表自己族裔<br />\n講唔過去"},{"pid":"297d69efe9fd5a12d8e0178297321c812a9dc6c4","tid":2070491,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"我希望如果佢有緣當選<br />\n麻煩叫班南亞𡃁仔有啲禮貌<br />\n咪鬼再係圖書館大叫"},{"pid":"450580d33aabf87a1ea84c603e96044231a6440c","tid":2070491,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e12911c22e417262003c7a41dccdd2543ff78c","tid":2070491,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"推阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9b084dbe91790123da1c2f6d3d71ecd707a2c4","tid":2070491,"uid":216828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5ec32e64b6fcf4d2cd31b72509c0b8956ae5b659","tid":2070491,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:57:19.000Z","msg":"好大左膠味，應該唔肯全否決<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6393f961b877835e83407bfa920f95fa3a52576","tid":2070491,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkg